column4: ProMetaS Machine Learning Metadata: Dataset Metadata
Storage Location of dataset. A pointer to the location where users can read the contents of the dataset. (Example: URL to a dataset)
Description of Database for every columns.(Data schema of dataset)
Statistics of the features, if applicable. Depending on data, it might be average value, standard deviation, etc.
Link to other dataset or related dataset.(if exists) For eg: A url to a dataset.
